<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM9.6">
<l>nāṟu naṟumpoḻil māliruñ cōlai nampikkunāṉ</l>
<l>nūṟu taṭāvilveṇ ṇeyvāy nērntu parāvivaittēṉ</l>
<l>nūṟu taṭāni ṟaintavak kāra vaṭicilcoṉṉē</l>
<l>ṉēṟu tiruvu ṭaiyāṉiṉṟu vantivai koḷḷuṅkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have worshipped the great [Lord] from [Tiru]māliruñcōlai</l>
<l rend="indent">with fragrant, redolent groves</l>
<l>[by] vowing to offer butter in a hundred big pots;</l>
<l>I have [also offered] through words a hundred big pots filled with sweetened rice.</l>
<l>Will He with a growing wealth come today and have these?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
